        [
          "While you do excellent work on mortals, your work on Kindred, no matter how well-executed, vanishes each sunset (unless you've used fire to create your patterns, but that of course comes with its own challenges). Find a way to make your Kindred work permanent. You know the Sabbat have a unique discipline to craft flesh, though you know no details beyond that. You've also heard rumors of a ritual, but again, know little. Find out more."
